       LDC-PRO-MCA SECTION.
       INI-LDC-PRO-MCA.
      * RENUEVA UNA CLF ACTIVADA, CONSERVANDO EL NUMERO DE LA ANTIGUA
           MOVE CLF-CAI-ICLF IN CLF-FLD TO MCA-CAI-ICLF IN MCA-VARI.
           MOVE CLF-IIC-ICLF IN CLF-FLD TO MCA-IIC-ICLF IN MCA-VARI.
           MOVE SPACES TO MCA-COD-SIST.
           MOVE SPACES TO MCA-COD-MENS.
           PERFORM LDC-LNK-MCA.
           IF MCA-COD-MENS NOT > SPACES
               MOVE 'DEU'   TO MSG-COD-SIST
               MOVE 'MCAOK' TO MSG-COD-MENS
           ELSE
               MOVE SCR-STAT-CON TO SCR-STAT
               MOVE MCA-COD-SIST IN MCA-VARI TO MSG-COD-SIST
               MOVE MCA-COD-MENS IN MCA-VARI TO MSG-COD-MENS.
           PERFORM GET-MSG.
           MOVE MSG-GLS-DESC TO FRM-MENS.
       FIN-LDC-PRO-MCA.
           EXIT.

